            <thetext>The grid decorator can be used to have an image background, which scales the inner
parts but leaves the border images intact.

In some cases it might not be necessary to resize the widget in both dimension. In this
case a HBox or VBox decorator, which uses three images and only scales the middle image,
would be sufficient. The decorators would be much more efficient since they require 6 DOM
elements less than the grid.</thetext>
